+
+# React import conventions
+
+- Use the namespace form: `import * as React from 'react'`.
+- Do not use individual named imports (`import { useState } from 'react'`)
+  in TanStack React Query test files.
+- Reference React explicitly (`React.createElement`, `React.useState`).
